<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Portfolio Admin</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4e73df;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fc;
            border-left: 1px solid #e3e6f0;
            border-right: 1px solid #e3e6f0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4e73df;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            background-color: #f8f9fc;
            border: 1px solid #e3e6f0;
            border-top: none;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Portfolio Admin!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for creating an account with Portfolio Admin. We're excited to have you on board!</p>
        
        <p>With your new account, you can:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Manage your portfolio projects</li>
            <li>View and respond to messages from visitors</li>
            <li>Update your profile and settings</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL || 'http://localhost:3000' %>/login" class="button">Get Started</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The Portfolio Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Portfolio. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you didn't create an account, please ignore this email or contact support.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
